      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/ex-taipei-mayor-ko-detained-amid-probe-of-property-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾民众党创始人柯文哲因担任台北市长期间的房地产重建项目腐败调查而被拘留。]]></description>
